{{Nihongo|'''Yuki Tanaka'''|田中 利幸|Tanaka Toshiyuki|extra=born May 26, 1949}} is a History Professor at [[Hiroshima University]].
He has written extensively about [[Comfort women|forced prostitution]] under the [[Japanese Empire]], as well as in [[Japan under US military rule]]. He also writes about the [[laws of warfare]]. 
